<gtr:grantReference>ESPA-EIRG-2011-166</gtr:grantReference><gtr:abstractText>This project is developing the concept of 'safe operating spaces' for development to prevent misguided actions causing loss or damage to ecosystem services which undermine long-term sustainability. Results will be drawn from an ongoing PFG project in the lower Yangtze basin and another project in Yunnan Province that combine conventional socio-economic records with reconstructed data for ecosystem services to show how close modern regions are to tipping points.</gtr:abstractText><gtr:fund><gtr:end>2013-11-01</gtr:end><gtr:funder url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/organisation/8A03ED41-E67D-4F4A-B5DD-AAFB272B6471"><gtr:id>8A03ED41-E67D-4F4A-B5DD-AAFB272B6471</gtr:id><gtr:name>NERC</gtr:name></gtr:funder><gtr:start>2013-02-01</gtr:start><gtr:type>INCOME_ACTUAL</gtr:type><gtr:valuePounds>49000</gtr:valuePounds></gtr:fund><gtr:output><gtr:artisticAndCreativeProductOutputs/><gtr:collaborationOutputs/><gtr:disseminationOutputs><gtr:disseminationOutput><gtr:description>International Planetary Boundaries Conference, Berlin, 24-25th April 2017</gtr:description><gtr:form>A talk or presentation</gtr:form><gtr:geographicReach>International</gtr:geographicReach><gtr:id>892AC9B2-9CC0-4C5B-9A4F-FD73BAAD2339</gtr:id><gtr:impact>Invited keynote lecture in Workshop 3: Building on Experience: Lessons learned from initial operationalizations</gtr:impact><gtr:outcomeId>5900bf1944bef7.61979566</gtr:outcomeId><gtr:partOfOfficialScheme>false</gtr:partOfOfficialScheme><gtr:primaryAudience>Policymakers/politicians</gtr:primaryAudience><gtr:url>https://www.pb-conference2017.de</gtr:url><gtr:year>2017</gtr:year></gtr:disseminationOutput><gtr:disseminationOutput><gtr:description>Safe operating spaces for regional rural development</gtr:description><gtr:form>A formal working group, expert panel or dialogue</gtr:form><gtr:geographicReach>International</gtr:geographicReach><gtr:id>B1B6A558-D8D7-45D8-8E52-1F4D32859DDF</gtr:id><gt